    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "你这个人，还真是不知“放弃”二字为何物呀。",
      "text_original": "諦めって言葉を知らない感じかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/rYTo4PyX4tJjpEYD0g0l06JXDXnCGp3I.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "噢……？",
      "text_original": "ふーん",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/jbtpZy0LobwCkTWFbJkT6ahtREA1nA59.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_Day_End",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "今日はこれで終わりかしら? お疲れ様だぞ、先生",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/4oMyIL7Yu5CESlU4LdOzuoFQJQjVarxU.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_Get_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "工作很努力嘛？那我就来夸夸你好了☆",
      "text_original": "なかなか頑張ったんじゃない?褒めて使わすぞ!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/qmqyeQV7jG45EfmZQxCKBgOcp675Fz3U.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_Get_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "这样应该会有些作用吧？",
      "text_original": "少しは役に立つんじゃない?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/qmjKhSRGsbwzi27u59za5hGqTBl3mcrF.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_Login_1",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "来确认一下进展吧。",
      "text_original": "進捗を確認してみましょうか",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/f8OfGD5QRJXKyibGdjUyVogpUikvTVzw.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_EventMission_Login_2",
      "category": "event",
      "text": "是来确认进展吗？有什么我可以帮你的？",
      "text_original": "確認に来たのね。何か手伝いましょうか?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/slKZLX9yeeRjXzuu84buVbbyHyvNU3FQ.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExSkill_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "嗯……真的不要紧吗？",
      "text_original": "ふーん?本当に大丈夫?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/RrY8ERFZTCKH4lTAcOlVtKEZWQPX1DPf.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExSkill_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "我本来没这个打算的……",
      "text_original": "ここまでするつもりはなかったけど",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/X8q3zud3wxy2P9Srx6To7reGTcdG7Uko.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExSkill_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "唉，看来真的没办法了呢~",
      "text_original": "ほんと、しょうがないんだから",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/ir51shsaX6OpLr375cFvWhOIcEXLMBCO.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExSkill_Level_1",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "结果还是会变成这样啊。",
      "text_original": "結局こうなっちゃうのよね",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/y9MOnyJoN9k8GoGzeCaaPOhGqgQl8j1h.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExSkill_Level_2",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "所以我不都说过了吗？",
      "text_original": "だから、言ったじゃない?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/r7NwAyqFLxyTob4RhVGSbs4VvRH4uH4v.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExSkill_Level_3",
      "category": "battle",
      "text": "好啦，你就放手去做吧？",
      "text_original": "好きにやってちょうだい",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/sqDP7FOy8lZfxAUqSlOTLzMRXmwhNXzQ.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_ExWeapon_Get",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "你也真是个奇怪的人呢。嗯，这当然不是贬义词哦。我一般不会信任没被我读过心的人……但对你的话，至少用不着怀疑吧？",
      "text_original": "あなたも変わってるわね。ああ、悪い意味ではないのよ。普通は頭の中を読んでない相手のことなんて信じないんだけど。疑ってない程度ってことにしておこうかしら。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/SGd7tU0M5Wlu1vOmE38MEeiTmluG1OTt.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Formation_In_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "我可不是冲锋陷阵的类型呀。",
      "text_original": "前に出るタイプじゃないんだけどなぁ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/SJaJgWBCET3kobqMpWMDkHjgwF5WPz55.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Formation_In_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "不过如果需要，我也不是不能帮你。",
      "text_original": "必要って言うならやってあげるけど",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/o4gCQvVCjFhPDAiS46Vxut6nFJpeuk2w.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Formation_Select",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "哼~？",
      "text_original": "何?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/eL6s99EcpSclundEbcjPxwFiwCKuImGh.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Gachaget",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "咦，我应该自我介绍过了啊……难道你不记得了？呵呵。",
      "text_original": "あら?自己紹介はしたはずだけど、もしかして覚えてないのかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/fzE4vsodV8srDpKAo9McoU8CrL6eQxD8.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感觉还不错嘛？那……要我为你做点什么吗？",
      "text_original": "悪くないかも?それで、私は何をすればいいのかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/wTWURRB4OQVtWrNuo5WDw4qucXnuNUAz.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我一般不喜欢欠人情……不过我会记住的。",
      "text_original": "仮は作らない主義だけど…覚えておくわね",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/zk1hnptfDEYBZpIQiPOaAeGP4ByrURiH.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "头脑好像清晰多了呢？",
      "text_original": "頭がすっきりするって感じ?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/NrwdcsMsSDxbyGXa20XeKbCo3RqtE4Nu.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感觉用起能力来好像轻松多了。……你很好奇吗？要不要来试一下？",
      "text_original": "なんだか能力を使いやすくなったかも…ん?気になるなら試してみる?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/cHqFkilyPB02K5COtzgdH29yRg3m1XMl.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Lobby_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师的工作，似乎跟我了解的那种差不多，但又有些区别呢。",
      "text_original": "先生のお仕事って私が知ってるものと同じようで違うのね",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/ajJOHsakCeco0n59iZ8o0X7Ye3QNQ66G.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Lobby_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "工作一定很辛苦吧……要不要我来帮帮你？……当然，是用“普通的方式”。",
      "text_original": "お仕事大変そうね?手伝いましょうか?もちろん、普通のやり方よ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/XpG4yxSrvhn6uM8xcEutuO5RhtPJX5Sh.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Lobby_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "其实，我现在还是有些头痛呢。",
      "text_original": "実はまだ今も頭がちょっと痛むのよ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/WjPLZoIDTTGzgP1mYTsEdAqSeYgX3tTQ.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Lobby_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "遥控器？它对我确实很重要……但不代表它本身有什么特别之处哦？",
      "text_original": "リモ君?確かに大事だけど、別にアレ自体に何かあるわけじゃないのよ?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/xpQ2UXGEFh6WEmsVlXuVY6McfaiZLtD5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Lobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "说起来，这里有什么美食吗？如果有推荐的店，可不可以带我去？",
      "text_original": "そういえばここって何が美味しいのかしら?おすすめのお店連れてってくれない?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/Uz4Rqa0dE0MSj9mmOfbPo5DVvHAfXUPk.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_LogIn_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "你来啦，老师。……人家等你很久了哦☆",
      "text_original": "いらっしゃい先生 こう見えて結構待ったんだぞ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/VMrU35NbDlTY6CvF1uu3NSiQCFVhvrwy.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_LogIn_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "嗯？我只是刚好待在这里而已。毕竟没有向导，我也不太想出门呢。",
      "text_original": "ん?なんとなくここに居ただけよ?ガイドもいないし、あんまり出かけたくなくって",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/wwClkT3cvZmIIJZl5F1q43JbkM4pn4KN.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……怎么了?",
      "text_original": "なに?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/5ub0rDCrqPRLy8pwJu7YXdwHLrZKcD1J.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "出什么事了吗？",
      "text_original": "どうかしたのかしら",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/e6rujRoKwgz8HOeCXyXTAqxKymhfKWjr.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "反正，我想这也是迟早的事。",
      "text_original": "いずれにせよ、いつかこうなることだったと思うのだけど?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/TA4ImJtbJQNZFJkzr7rBXi7Kz1uScJMY.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……对不对？",
      "text_original": "そうでしょ?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/epKRCTXBHGOqz87w0xjGbaRimLjCRbZV.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "遥控器？ ……你确定要问这个吗？",
      "text_original": "リモコン?それ、聞いちゃおう?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/H51dJGACmI1MXSWXkDiau5bjf2v4zz7B.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "不觉得这样有些欠考虑吗?",
      "text_original": "ちょっと気配りが足りないかも",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/gqSpql7L2hfEhCS77HMD5x7MF5anKj8j.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "如果一件事女孩子不想说……",
      "text_original": "女の子が話そうとしていないのだろう",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/9GMvtNVKavPbAQulRdHKdYu3GYrUpfF6.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "非要打破砂锅问到底可不好哦☆",
      "text_original": "無理に聞こうとしちゃダメだぞ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/3teHCcdAAqPFl1Ou7lTLvnFnbbDphGm3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "你什么都没看见，什么都没听见，什么都没发生。",
      "text_original": "いい?あなたは何も見ていないし、そもそも何も起きてなかった。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/PI8NDymP1eRBjSk9X1VA5Z5vXpVlb3rp.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_MemorialLobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……对吧，老师？",
      "text_original": "そうよね 先生",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/3hSuetfursNjlzZfcpzA4zXeTFMK4SEp.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Relationship_Up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "你对其他人也是这样吗？呵呵……看来你相当有人气力呢。",
      "text_original": "あなたって他の人にもこんな感じなの?これはきっと相当な人気力ね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/xSi6w3yJpRQNg6LAT4Hf5uo2JtEitWzD.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Relationship_Up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "唔……这也是出于“老师”的身份吗？",
      "text_original": "ん? これも先生だからかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/8ysUfvxBNJ4UOs2DTl86evz8SwWbGEiX.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Relationship_Up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "偶尔会想读读看你脑子里的想法呢。……啊，我只是说说，又不是真的试过，你不用担心。",
      "text_original": "たまには頭の中を覗きたいなぁと思っているのよ？あ、まだやってないから心配しないでちょうだい",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/xxssfxBRfXr0W0nx7zmsLOTjgMV3eHjR.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Relationship_Up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我说……你对区区外来者是不是也太好了？",
      "text_original": "ちょっと、よそ者相手にやりすぎじゃないかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/DbHnUQdvKswQigqskKGqxXOo1OISaGL9.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Season_Birthday_Player",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "今天是老师的生日吧？唔，该怎么为你庆祝呢。……顺便问一下，你有没有想和哪个人一起度过今天呢？",
      "text_original": "先生のお誕生日よね?どう祝ってあげましょう。ちなみに一緒に過ごしたいことがいるかしら?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/nsE84nv57f2DLXn9W6AWPIyq7QpjGKMn.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Season_Halloween",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "外面真吵呀。嗯……不过在这里应该不要紧。",
      "text_original": "外が騒がしいわね。まあ、ここなら構わないけど。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/q4srdIGSZftXbvy9KAVXnkuP1fqrLlrL.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Season_NewYear",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "新年快乐，老师。……在这里，也是这样打招呼的没错吧？",
      "text_original": "あけましておめでとう先生 ここでもこの挨拶であってるのかしら",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E9%A3%9F%E8%9C%82%20%E6%93%8D%E7%A5%88/gSLZZ9ZjnB24rJ8FDgCrEe5aHyniQnb4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9997_Season_Xmas",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "圣诞节啊……老师，你都当过几次圣诞老人呢？",
      "text_original": "クリスマスね。先生は何回サントになったのかしら?",
